{"tid":1192934,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"原來深圳歡樂城海岸都幾值得去！","createTime":"2019-06-08T16:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T16:38:21.000Z","uid":197098,"like":5,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"968dbe034745496be13b7ba968819a9c23e4170a","tid":1192934,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"今天去了深圳一日遊，香港的地方已經去得七七八八，朋友提議去深圳，所以今日試下，歡樂海岸都幾值得去，室內是大型購物廣場，室外是最吸引-好似另一個世界咁，又有煙花睇，嘢食又有特色和抵食，夜景燈飾最靚！從落馬州跟住地鐵地圖坐地鐵去，既方便又快捷，幾個字就到，坐的士都係幾十蚊。Coco購物公園也去過，夜晚燈飾都吸引！"},{"pid":"e4e15610ee7a8f6abf5b26704883cf95d06e7507","tid":1192934,"uid":55493,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"去吓新疆西藏啦，好地方嚟"},{"pid":"d150d8fee4ec3594e80630d117dcb609bf1a1339","tid":1192934,"uid":55493,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:22:25.000Z","msg":"正過深圳，唔係老點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc819ab47239fa665190b990c7f04966fe3406d4","tid":1192934,"uid":140639,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"祝你上左去落唔番來 你隻支那猪"},{"pid":"89b0105496018171f5a4fe09efe3ab999fddf846","tid":1192934,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:32:26.000Z","msg":"上去食兔肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bdbaa1ee9867a103bb85bb6d35789ee7ae0757","tid":1192934,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"香港的地方已經去得七七八八<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔撚信阿柒頭，當人ON9都有個譜啦"},{"pid":"0fb7f8c18cd5de4ada889897eb9bcfd0cd5a7788","tid":1192934,"uid":21378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"其實又係果堆舖頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n好快悶."},{"pid":"73f9aee1df7a87890e0f5ee1b4892f3a915cd53e","tid":1192934,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"